article_title: No One Injured In School Bus Crash In Norman - News9.com - Oklahoma City, OK - News, Weather, Video and Sports
article_text:
Emergency crews are on the scene of a collision involving a school bus in Norman, Oklahoma, Tuesday morning.

According to Norman police, at 7:35 a.m., crews responded to a collision involving a school bus and another vehicle in the 800 block of Barber Ave.

Police said four children were on the bus during the crash. No one was injured.
